d/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-053.jpg?height=427&width=401&top__y=980&top__x=468","line":1060,"embedded":true},{"title":"|764x188","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-055.jpg?height=256&width=1043&top__y=1369&top__x=362","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"0, \\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{5}\\.$ )；\n(4) $\\triangle F M N$ 周长的最小值为 $\\sqrt{2}+1$.\n\n其中正确结论的为（）\nA. (1)(2)\nB. (2)(3)\nC. (3)(4)\nD. (1)(4)\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-078.jpg?height=427&width=404&top__y=980&top__x=466","line":1534},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$\nD. $(-\\infty, 2) \\cup(2,+\\infty)$\n\n#### 10.2.2 【 练 1-1\n\n圆 $x^{2}+y^{2}+4 \\sin \\theta \\cdot x+4 \\cos \\theta \\cdot y+1=0$ 的半径等于 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.3 【 练 1-2\n\n已知 $A(-2,2) ， B(2,6)$ ，则以 $A B$ 为直径的圆的标准方程为 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.4 【 练 1-3\n\n正方形草地 $A B C D$ 边长 $1.2 ， E$ 到 $A B ， A D$ 距离为 $0.2 ， F$ 到 $B C ， C D$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2226},{"title":"                                                             | 201x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=201&top__y=1293&top__x=738","line":2683,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 212x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=212&top__y=1513&top__x=723","line":2684,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 201x156","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=156&width=201&top__y=1742&top__x=738","line":2685,"embedded":true},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3034,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3503}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1c51oxn","at":1769671106767}},"smart_blocks:01-数学教学/讲义/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】修改版本.md#": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04352764,-0.00503088,0.06357807,0.01862683,0.03766482,-0.01080614,-0.0716439,0.04129852,0.02762647,0.05662715,0.03210181,-0.07246335,0.03054132,0.00372167,0.00686686,-0.00542296,-0.0169042,-0.03757372,-0.04367116,-0.0126742,0.13057597,-0.014608,-0.00920353,-0.06004944,0.04990714,0.05742944,-0.00375208,-0.08961076,-0.01672999,-0.20318355,-0.00438644,0.08716951,0.05487025,0.03094138,0.0228956,-0.05353153,-0.00195373,0.07370248,-0.00826231,0.04979086,0.01511266,0.06838558,0.0112577,0.00815337,-0.00578357,-0.06933546,-0.06735048,-0.02107361,0.0340433,-0.02565528,-0.04334287,-0.02736484,0.00624298,0.02924244,-0.03160583,0.01326953,0.03885796,0.00426479,0.03044527,0.03975575,0.01602101,0.00110676,-0.24126995,0.04876006,0.05911817,-0.0240586,-0.01538777,-0.03946953,0.02560322,0.0743879,-0.02158488,0.00049324,0.0037386,0.01065226,-0.00382462,-0.02513571,0.00318669,-0.07694161,-0.0238378,-0.04662529,-0.03178835,0.08396076,-0.03991874,-0.00731348,-0.01067802,0.05048697,0.00414187,-0.07805946,0.00668521,-0.01286145,0.00113706,-0.02311097,-0.02510523,0.01914571,-0.07741433,-0.04432035,0.01581153,0.00418146,-0.0083556,0.07986816,-0.04199829,0.00133784,0.03972534,0.002436,-0.03712772,0.04144663,-0.00747496,-0.09247077,-0.01257108,-0.00329943,0.01468742,-0.01340298,0.09802865,-0.03634391,-0.02593715,-0.00063011,-0.03349924,-0.03914221,-0.01837999,0.02160637,-0.00120495,0.01375526,0.03204292,-0.00170487,0.02837024,-0.02406257,-0.01175725,0.02522879,-0.00350249,0.03555222,0.02339462,-0.0013631,-0.03720973,-0.03665873,-0.023654